"# Multilingual AI eBook App

This is a trilingual conversational eBook reader app powered by GPT-4o, built for children aged 4â€“8. It supports stories in English, Spanish, and Basque and enables children to interact with the story characters through real-time conversation.

## How to Run

1. Clone the repo:
\`\`\`
git clone https://github.com/tthomas840/multiling_agent_ebook_app.git
\`\`\`

2. Navigate to the backend and run Flask:
\`\`\`
cd backend
python app.py
\`\`\`

3. Navigate to the frontend and start the app:
\`\`\`
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
\`\`\`

Make sure you have an OpenAI API key and MongoDB connection string set in a .env file.
